When used in this subchapter the term “person” includes partnerships, corporations, and associations.
(Sept. 8, 1916, ch. 463, title VIII, § 800, 39 Stat. 798.)</akn:p></akn:content></akn:section></akn:body></akn:act></akn:akomaNtoso>